## Solver-log signatures to confirm wiring

| Signature | From | Meaning |
|---|---|---|
| `LC-06 rest replanning: rt_replannable=True, ct_replannable=True` | service.py | Phase A flags set from trigger payload. |
| `lock_allocations=true: N blocks (replannable excluded: ['RT Jour de repos', 'CT Jour de compensation'])` | service.py | Phase A sanitize let RT/CT through to `exclude_calendar_types`. |
| `[LC_06] Adding rest-day allocation: …` | lc_06_rest_days_allocation.py | LC-06 reached the body — flags recognized. |
| `[LC_06] Priority-1 anchor applied to N resource(s) on day 0` | lc_06_rest_days_allocation.py | Partition-boundary anchor carried over; only on partition #2+. |
| `[LC_06] Overlap (demand↔rest) constraints: N` | lc_06_rest_days_allocation.py | Overlap enforcement applied. |
| `[LC_06] Target constraints: rt=N, ct=N, combined=N` | lc_06_rest_days_allocation.py | Per-month targets seeded. |
| `[LC_08_monthly_rest_v2] SKIPPED — LC-06 rest-days allocation active` | model.py | Phase K gate fired. |
| `LC-06 rest-day rows emitted: RT=N, CT=N` | model._extract_solution | Output stage added synthetic rows. |
| `Saved N normalized assignments for plan PLAN-... (by type: {'DEMAND': X, 'RT': Y, 'CT': Z})` | service.py | Phase H normalized insert succeeded with new column. |

